ru.myx.io

Class DataInputByteArrayFast

  • Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • ru.myx.io.DataInputByteArrayFast
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.DataInput, AutoCloseable

    public final class DataInputByteArrayFast
extends java.io.InputStream
implements java.io.DataInput
    Super fast, reusable but doesn't hold and extra buffers and fields, in any case faster than ByteArrayInputStream and DataInputStream.
    Author:
    myx
